ComicInfo.Summary: Katchoo's hunt for Stephanie, a Parker Girl on the run, takes her to the Florida Keys and a hair-raising visit with Stephanie's... hmm, how do we put this... eccentric family. Meanwhile, Francine grows restless with Katchoo's extended absence and begins to suspect she might need help.
